data.description: Welcome to your new home located close to the Snake River walking path and minutes away from all things Mini-Cassia has to offer! This absolutely beautiful home has two living spaces, 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms and so much storage. The master bath is brand new and absolutely GORGEOUS along with a brand new furnace/AC system with a transferable warranty. You cannot help but instantly fall in love with all the space this home has to off as well as the instant cozy feeling of "Home." You do not want to miss calling this beauty yours today, call for a showing!
